{"id": 546, "genre": 1001, "title": "你为什么爱弹幕？", "description": "以免憋出内伤。", "record_count": 5875, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183616efATkxFSMyOC7hBt.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-07T01:11:16Z", "options": [{"id": 16641, "content": "爽！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214264}, {"id": 15106, "content": "良辰只有一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231481}, {"id": 15362, "content": "弹幕有时候比节目更精彩", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193001}, {"id": 15618, "content": "志同道合的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236212}, {"id": 15874, "content": "弹幕中会出现神吐槽", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238046}, {"id": 15107, "content": "没看过弹幕不足以谈人参～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207286}, {"id": 21507, "content": "真理是掌握在多数人手里的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278210}, {"id": 15366, "content": "假装自己不是一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234148}, {"id": 15622, "content": "吐槽的能量值", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211126qs8oEfB76GTv01Pw.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236313}, {"id": 15111, "content": "寻开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228634}, {"id": 15112, "content": "神烦弹幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202945}, {"id": 15624, "content": "想看些我没注意到的细节", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233672}, {"id": 15114, "content": "感觉我不是一个人，有人懂我的世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215699}, {"id": 15115, "content": "无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118917}, {"id": 15116, "content": "一人看恐怖片时不会被吓到", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231567}, {"id": 15884, "content": "因为我话多", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211128DIcwULCOqfApNQFy.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237999}, {"id": 15118, "content": "因为一些搞笑的地方总能被弹幕挖掘，有很多吐槽人才在上面", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231575}, {"id": 15120, "content": "学习吐槽技能", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225115}, {"id": 15632, "content": "一个人在家看视频，但有种身边有人陪的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 210646}, {"id": 15634, "content": "弹幕护体", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235090}, {"id": 15892, "content": "可以分享笑点泪点，当然很有可能把泪点逗成笑点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236534}, {"id": 15125, "content": "这是一种坐山观虎斗的快感", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 230269}, {"id": 15893, "content": "男生都有神评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227722}, {"id": 16919, "content": "有时候我只想知道有没有人跟我想的一样，没神经病就好～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215202}, {"id": 15128, "content": "电视剧某刻无聊啰嗦的时候，我才关注弹幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212563}, {"id": 15385, "content": "难道看视频不就是为了看弹幕？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227829}, {"id": 15899, "content": "总有些神回复", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236996}, {"id": 15132, "content": "变废为宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 16157, "content": "看恐怖片提前做好心理准备", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241829}, {"id": 21022, "content": "我，      不爱弹幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207871}, {"id": 15135, "content": "没人说话？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114820}, {"id": 16159, "content": "随时可以吐槽", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241680}, {"id": 16928, "content": "一起边聊边看视频，不！孤！单！???", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250495}, {"id": 15138, "content": "剧透多，死全家很过瘾！", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004705vGXK25BIO4qtd7h6.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205887}, {"id": 15139, "content": "感觉有很多人在陪自己一起看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 218359}, {"id": 15141, "content": "可以帮你找到志同道合的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229824}, {"id": 16421, "content": "我只看看，不说话，你们随意。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245433}, {"id": 15142, "content": "及時享樂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227828}, {"id": 15143, "content": "及時享樂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227828}, {"id": 15144, "content": "及時享樂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227828}, {"id": 15145, "content": "我有想让米认识我", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222887}, {"id": 15658, "content": "水一帖", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235298}, {"id": 17962, "content": "看网友狠狠吐槽！", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211226pEqyAjQomxW4FI3B.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256526}, {"id": 15147, "content": "为了不会感觉是一个人在看", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228537}, {"id": 15150, "content": "不同人的想法，像是在交流", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231839}, {"id": 15151, "content": "高能预警！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179498}, {"id": 15408, "content": "更接地气…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234504}, {"id": 15920, "content": "因为我爱吐槽啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238776}, {"id": 16176, "content": "并不爱弹幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242123}, {"id": 15154, "content": "呵呵哒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231414}]}